summary:
Independent interim professional with multidisciplinary experience in procurement, logistics, sales, finance (O2C) and customer care.
Proven successful in international operating businesses.

Excellent communication skills, analytical, motivator and multilingual;
(Dutch, English, German and Polish).

Specialties: Sourcing, Relationship management, Supply chain finance, Demand / Sales planning, Business analytics.

Prince2 certified,
Certified Six-Sigma Green Belt.
